    "While crypto jacking attacks are comparatively less frequent, they still pose a considerable risk, accounting for 28% of total attacks.",
    "Encrypted threats and IoT attacks are relatively rare, accounting for 4% and 66% respectively.",
    "DENIAL OF SERVICE (DOS) ATTACKSDoS attacks involve the deliberate flooding of a network with false requests, disrupting normal business operations.",
    "Users are unable to perform routine tasks like accessing email, websites, or online accounts when targeted by these attacks.",
    "While most DoS attacks do not result in data loss and can be resolved without paying a ransom, they impose significant costs on organizations, including time, money, and resource allocation."
